That means, first of all, that there is something very special about the U.=
S. Our network of universities, tech companies, and government labs constit=
utes the largest concentration of top-tier research talent on planet Earth.=
 Talented people flow between these centers of innovation, exchanging ideas=
, building on each other=E2=80=99s ideas, cross-fertilizing, etc. The U.S. =
stopped being the =E2=80=9Cworkshop of the world=E2=80=9D long ago, but we =
are still the world=E2=80=99s research park.=20
